To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private Engulfing _engulfing;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_engulfing = Engulfing(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_engulfing.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "Engulfing Period", _engulfing.Period);
    Plot("My Indicators", "Engulfing Current", _engulfing.Current);
}
